videos.description: Payton Pritchard appears to injure his leg on a rebound and is carried off the floor in the first quarter.

videos.description: Kemba Walker puts the moves on three Sixers defenders to get to the basket, then gives a sly smile as he runs back on defense.

videos.headline: Kemba sauces up the Sixers' defense for a layup

videos.description: Ben Simmons anticipates the pass to get the steal, then hurries down the court to flush a two-handed dunk.

videos.description: Despite Jaylen Brown going for 42 points and 9 rebounds, the 76ers willed their way to a 122-110 win over the Celtics behind Joel Embiid's 38 points and 11 rebounds.
